PrecisAppointment of JAMES K. BARTLEMAN as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Nauru and to the Republic of Vanuata, and as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of the Marshall Islands and to the Federated States of Micronesia, with residence in Canberra; LUCIE EDWARDS as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Mauritius and to the Republic of Namibia, with residence in Pretoria; RODNEY IRWIN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Uzbekistan, with residence in Moscow; RICHARD MANN as Ambassador of Canada to the State of Qatar, with residence in Kuwait; PETER McKELLAR as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Lithuania, and to the Republic of Estonia, with residence in Riga; JOHN ROBINSON as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of the Bahamas and to Belize, with residence in Kingston; and JAMES WALL as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Mozambique, with residence in Harare.
